title: Bye, Bye, Bye

[intro]
(Am) Ooh-ooh (G)Ooh-ooh (F)Ooh-ooh (Hey hey)
(Dm) Bye bye, bye, bye (Am)bye! (Am)

(F) I know that I can't (G)take no more, it ain't no lie

(F) Might sound crazy but it (G)ain't no lie

(Am) Just hit me with the truth

[chorus]

(Am) I don't wanna (G)make it tough (Make it tough)
